eft class=m><span class=title> Just for reference:</span><hr size=1> Here's an updated list of what and where.  Not taking credit for the info (some from Safehouse on previous posts and some from other sites), just compiling it in one neat spot. Let's fill in the last couple of slots and see what the rewards are <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
(BTW, if there is already a thread for this I apologize. Search failed to find a related thread.)<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>Holin Aeridia's Crypt:</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Aeridia Family Signet Ring:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Comes off a Neculas smuggler in Marus Seru<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Sealed Golden Scroll Tube:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Mark Blotter, the general spell vendor in Shadow Haven midst area sells the sealed golden scroll tube for 1000 gp. <br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Faded Silver Embroidered Robe:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Rolktim Cogtop is standing behind Ebben's tavern, loc approx -1243, -636. He dropped the Faded Silver Embroidered Robe from the Holin Aeridia crypt. Light blue to 56, no faction hits.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Tarnished Copper Runed Wand:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>Raien Taliker's Crypt:</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Ancient Ornate Combine Dagger:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Ornate Combine dagger dropped off named female bandit in the Paludal Caves.Her name is Maricella Slithra and she spawns at -1424, 1374. It is supposedly a rare drop. She spawns just outside the camp with Yelloweyes, close to Shadowhaven.  She has a placeholder bandit.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Taliker Family Signet Ring:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Faded Portrait of a Lady:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Near the bank upstairs in the northeast corner of Shadow Haven is an inn, and there's an NPC in one of the rooms who talks about buying and selling paintings. Name is Pietro Guiccini hes a naked high elf and he is at loc +1468 +66 -45 in Shadowhaven library by the inn  He doesn't have any bracketed text, but if you say something like &quot;I would like to buy a portrait,&quot; he'll tell you that for 1000 gold pieces he'll sell you one. So I gave him 1000 gp (he's not a vendor) and he gave me a lore no drop &quot;Faded Portrait of A Lady&quot; with no stats (looks like a playing card.)   <br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Antique Platinum Medal:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Killed Ebben Today. He conned light blue at level 55. None of the other mobs in the bar joined in. No faction hit at all. He dropped an Antique Platinum Medal.  When he died he listed 2 other names. No doubt they hold the other items from the Rainen Talimar crypt. These names are.... Rolkim and Missy. <br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>Shoeon Malicus Crypt:</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Gold Embroidered Kilt:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Missy McElle is found in a corner of Fungus Grove's outpost section (the section before the one with Ebben's tavern, her loc is approx -1130, -800). She dropped the Gold Embroidered Kilt from the Shoen Malicus crypt. She was light blue to 56, no faction hits.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Silver Embroidered Tabard:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Ancient Ceremonial Warhammer:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Old Sealed Medicine Pouch:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
